  "Title": "An update for perl-DBI is now available for openEuler-22.03-LTS-SP4,openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP1,openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP3,openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP4,openEuler-20.03-LTS-SP4",
